package lesson2

import kotlin.jvm.internal.Intrinsics
import kotlin.jvm.internal.Intrinsics.checkParameterIsNotNull

public class OddOccurrencesInArray {
    public fun solution(array: IntArray): Int {
        Intrinsics.checkParameterIsNotNull(array, "array")
        val length = array.size
        var result = 0
        for (i in 0 until length) {
            result = result xor array[i]
        }
        return result
    }
}

fun main() {
    val array = intArrayOf(9, 3, 9, 3, 9, 7, 7)
    val solution = OddOccurrencesInArray()
    val result = solution.solution(array)
    println(result)
}
